Description:
  Scaffolds a host app component with a ClassVariants theme module and ERB partial.
  Components are rendered using the appui() helper.

Examples:
  bin/rails generate kiso:app_component pricing_card

    Creates:
      app/themes/pricing_card.rb
      app/views/components/_pricing_card.html.erb

  bin/rails generate kiso:app_component pricing_card --sub-parts header footer

    Creates:
      app/themes/pricing_card.rb
      app/themes/pricing_card_header.rb
      app/themes/pricing_card_footer.rb
      app/views/components/_pricing_card.html.erb
      app/views/components/pricing_card/_header.html.erb
      app/views/components/pricing_card/_footer.html.erb

Usage:
  appui(:pricing_card) { "Content" }

  appui(:pricing_card) do
    appui(:pricing_card, :header) { "Title" }
    appui(:pricing_card, :footer) { "Actions" }
  end
